Package org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.stellaris

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FlashLoaderCommand
    FlashLoaderCommand represents datagrams that begin with a distinguished command byte
    FlashLoaderDatagram
    {link FlashLoaderDatagram} represents the core packet structure of transmissions to and from the flash loader.
    FlashLoaderDownloadCommand
    This command is sent to the flash loader to indicate where to store data and how many bytes will be sent by the COMMAND_SEND_DATA commands that follow.
    FlashLoaderGetStatusCommand
    This command returns the status of the last command that was issued.
    FlashLoaderGetStatusResponse
    FlashLoaderGetStatusResponse codifies the response packet to a FlashLoaderGetStatusCommand.
    FlashLoaderManager
    FlashLoaderManager manages the process of writing a new firmware image.
    FlashLoaderPingCommand
    This command simply accepts the command and sets the global status to success.
    FlashLoaderResetCommand
    This command is used to tell the flash loader device to reset.
    FlashLoaderSendDataCommand
    This command should only follow a COMMAND_DOWNLOAD command or another COMMAND_SEND_DATA command if more data is needed.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    FlashLoaderProtocolException
    FlashLoaderProtocolExceptions are thrown when we've encountered a situation that lies outside the bounds of the flash updating protocol as it was documented.
